  "body": "introduced by https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/15204\r\nCC: @alwx \r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce:\r\n1. Open a chat screen with no previous messages\r\n2. Tap on the input field (composer) to focus on it.\r\n\r\n### Actual result:\r\nWhen focusing on the input field in an empty chat screen on Android, a flickering effect occurs. \r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/52490791/cd945195-c807-430b-ba38-a422f9946204\r\n\r\n### Expected result:\r\nFocusing on the input field in an empty chat screen on Android should not result in flickering\r\n\r\n### Devices:\r\n- Real device: Pixel 7a, Android 13\r\n- Android Studio: Pixel XL API 29",
